<list_item><loc_56><loc_126><loc_439><loc_159>2 In light of the release of the Php 5,000 teaching allowance per teacher for SY 2024-2025, this school year shall be considered a transition period. Strict implementation of this Order shall commence in SY 2025-2026 and continue in subsequent school years.</list_item>
